OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773954350
OL,3,CHospital to introduce body-worn
OL,4,Ccameras to combat attacks on staff
OL,6,FBody-worn cameras are being introduced
OL,7,Ffor staff working in the emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment of the Ulster Hospital in
OL,9,Fan attempt to combat an increase in
OL,10,Fviolent attacks and abuse.
OL,12,FThe South Eastern Trust said there
OL,13,Fwere 1,911 incidents of violence and
OL,14,Faggression towards their staff between
OL,15,FApril and December last year.
OL,17,FThe trust hopes the introduction of
OL,18,Fthe cameras at the hospital in
OL,19,FDundonald from Monday will help to
OL,20,Fimprove staff safety.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
