FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773954350
OL,3,CHospital to introduce body-worn
OL,4,Ccameras to combat attacks on staff
OL,6,FStaff who choose to wear the devices
OL,7,Fwill attach them to their uniforms and
OL,8,Fcan activate the cameras if they feel
OL,9,Funsafe.
OL,11,FOnce activated, the cameras will
OL,12,Frecord both video and audio.
OL,14,FStaff who are wearing the cameras will
OL,15,Fannounce when the device is being
OL,16,Factivated and when recording has
OL,17,Fstopped.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773954350
OL,3,CHospital to introduce body-worn
OL,4,Ccameras to combat attacks on staff
OL,6,FMaggie Magowan, clinical manager for
OL,7,Femergency medicine, said: "Every day,
OL,8,Four staff come to work with one
OL,9,Fpurpose, to care for people who may be
OL,10,Ffrightened, in pain or going through
OL,11,Fsome of their most difficult moments
OL,12,Fof their lives.
OL,14,F"Providing safe, compassionate and
OL,15,Frespectful care is at the heart of
OL,16,Feverything we do.
OL,18,F"It is deeply distressing that we
OL,19,Fcontinue to see increasing levels of
OL,20,Fviolence and aggression directed
OL,21,Ftowards our staff.
OL,26,@oD@[OUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773954350
OL,3,CHospital to introduce body-worn
OL,4,Ccameras to combat attacks on staff
OL,6,F"No-one should ever feel afraid while
OL,7,Fdoing their job, especially when that
OL,8,Fjob is to support and protect some of
OL,9,Fthe most vulnerable members of our
OL,10,Fcommunity."
OL,12,FMarc Neil, director of unscheduled
OL,13,Fcare, medicine and cancer services,
OL,14,Fsaid: "The introduction of body-worn
OL,15,Fcameras is a supportive measure
OL,16,Fdesigned to help keep our staff safe.
OL,18,F"These cameras will only be activated
OL,19,Fif a member of staff feels unsafe or a
OL,20,Fsituation begins to escalate.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]vD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773954350
OL,3,CHospital to introduce body-worn
OL,4,Ccameras to combat attacks on staff
OL,6,F"Our goal is always to deescalate and
OL,7,Fto prevent harm, and we hope the
OL,8,Fpresence of these cameras will
OL,9,Freassure staff while also acting as a
OL,10,Fdeterrent to aggressive behaviour.
OL,12,F"We want our teams to know that their
OL,13,Fwellbeing matters deeply to us.
OL,15,F"We are committed to doing everything
OL,16,Fwe can to make their working
OL,17,Fenvironment as safe and supportive as
OL,18,Fpossible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
